SUMMARY:Taste of Improv - Improv Open Mic Georgetown Art Attack
DTSTAMP:20260325T064636Z
DTSTART:20260411T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Whether you’re a student\\\, a pro\\\, or just checking out the
	 Art Attack\\\, this is your chance to take the stage\\\, make bold choice
	s\\\, and have a blast doing it.\\n\\nJoin Unexpected Productions Improv S
	chool as we join Georgetown’s ART ATTACK with a spontaneous showcase of im
	prov talent. Bring your squad\\\, support each other\\\, and celebrate the
	 joy of live\\\, unfiltered performance.\\nHit the Georgetown Art Attack\\
	\, then head over to the Improv School.\\nCome for the art. Stay for the i
	mprov. See you there!\n\nhttps://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/taste
	-of-improv-improv-open-mic-georgetown-art-attack-2-2-2-2/2026-04-11/\n\nFr
	om Unexpected Productions
